===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: tāotiè

===Idiom===
'''[[饕]][[餮]]'''

# a stylized design frequently found on ancient bronzes interpreted variously as one animal facing out or two animals facing each other.
# a gourmand; a glutton
# a legendary animal

